  11 Aug 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Sync eclass with portage tree.  See bug #137423 for more information.

  09 Aug 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
